  script_tag(name:"vuldetect", value:"Checks if a vulnerable package version is present on the target host.");

  script_tag(name:"insight", value:"Updated davfs2 package fixes security vulnerability:

Davfs2, a filesystem client for WebDAV, calls the function system()
insecurely while is setuid root. This might allow a privilege escalation.
(CVE-2013-4362)");

  script_tag(name:"affected", value:"'davfs2' package(s) on Mageia 2, Mageia 3.");

  script_tag(name:"solution", value:"Please install the updated package(s).");

